data.description: Panoramic Siuslaw River, ocean and jetty views along with spectacular sunsets await you in this beautiful custom fully furnished 3 bedroom, 3.5 bath great room with wall of windows and sliders to enjoy the outdoors. Vaulted knotty pine ceilings, granite counters, Viking professional stainless appliances. Master suite on main level, large walk-in shower, jetted tub, granite. Guest en-suites on lower level, one with mini bar. Bonus room, lots of storage, finished double garage. 2023-10-12
